This paper discusses the design challenges of mmWave massive MIMO systems relying on low-resolution ADCs, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and communications (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), computer architecture (cs.AR), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
